title: VMware Workstation Pro 14.1.0 Build 7370693 With Keygen [Latest!
description:
VMware Workstation software features:

Ability to run switch programs only with drag and drop
Full and consistent support of PXE
Multi-level position management
Configure the software as a virtual network, live images
Integrated implementation of Windows, Linux, Netware, Solaris X86 as a virtual network
Multiple monitor display capabilities
Supports MP3 players and USB devices
Supports HD surround sound 7.1
Bluetooth support
Creating virtual machines up to 8 virtual processors or 8 virtual cores, 2 terabytes of virtual hard disk and up to 64 GB of memory per virtual machine to run more applications.
Support for 32-bit and 64-bit systems in Linux and Windows
The ability to display the operating system before it runs
Strong and powerful propulsion environment with basic texture
Better 3D graphics
Supports OpenGL and Shader Model 3
Supports VMware vSphere 4 as a guest OS
Configuring virtual systems for multi-core cpu usage
Print on a virtual system without the need to install a printer driver using ThinPrint
Security of virtual machines with 128bit encryption
